      <title>尽管中国股票出现反弹，MSCI 仍将更多中国股票剔除出指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/msci-ousts-more-chinese-stocks-from-indexes-despite-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明晟公司进一步将中国股票从其全球基准指数中下调，凸显出尽管中国市场近期有所反弹，但对投资者的吸引力正在减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/msci-ousts-more-chinese-stocks-from-indexes-despite-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:48:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾即将退出监管机构的黑钱“灰名单”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/philippines-nears-exit-from-watchdog-s-dirty-money-gray-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾可能最早于下周从全球黑钱名单中被除名，这对这个东南亚国家来说是一个潜在的推动，因为该国正在努力推行改革，打击洗钱和恐怖主义融资风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/philippines-nears-exit-from-watchdog-s-dirty-money-gray-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 01:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
